===Noun===
'''glass'''

# A solid, transparent [[substance]] made by melting [[sand]] with a mixture of [[soda]], [[potash]] and [[lime]].
# A [[container]] used for carrying [[liquid]]s for [[drink]]ing made of glass.
# (Physics) [[Amorphous]] (non-[[crystalline]]) substance.

